\f0\b0\fs30 \cf0 You travel north into a more central region of Africa. You\'92d climbed mountains before, but this is the first time you\'92re climbing something as ambitious as Kilimanjaro. You decide to rest up at a guesthouse with the other climbers the night before your climb. You have a grand time, almost as enjoyable as the view from the top of the mountain the next day. The day after, you go on a safari and spot lions, a rhino, and even a leopard. What\'92s more, a friend you\'92d made at Victoria Falls just so happens to be on your tour bus! You decide to go scuba diving with him. However, you don\'92t realize he\'92s a novice diver, and he tires too easily and almost drags the two of you out to sea. You both survive, but your friend vows to never dive again.
